Interface IPObjectList<T extends IPObject>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.List<T>

    IPObjectList.EmptyList, PObjectList, PObjectTypedList

    public interface IPObjectList<T extends IPObject>
extends java.util.List<T>
    Collection, which holds IPObjects. The purpose of this collection is to provide controll on resolving of the objects.
